{
"#name"
:
{
"abox"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"AI Agent Box - Docker 容器管理模块"
,
"en"
:
"AI Agent Box - Docker container management module"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"abox 是一个用于管理 AI Agent Docker 容器的命令行工具。\n它提供了快速启动、停止、重启容器的能力，以及通过 tmux、ssh、exec 等方式与容器交互的功能。\n适用于本地开发和测试 AI 编程代理（如 Claude Code、Codex、OpenCode）的场景。\n"
,
"en"
:
"abox is a command-line tool for managing AI Agent Docker containers.\nIt provides the ability to quickly start, stop, and restart containers,\nas well as interact with containers via tmux, ssh, exec, etc.\nSuitable for local development and testing of AI programming agents (e.g., Claude Code, Codex, OpenCode).\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"快速开始：\n1. 启动容器：`x abox start`\n2. 连接到容器，并打开 tmux 名为 claude 的会话：`x abox tmux :claude`\n3. 停止容器：`x abox stop`\n"
,
"en"
:
"Quick Start:\n1. Start container: `x abox start`\n2. Connect to container and open tmux session named claude: `x abox tmux :claude`\n3. Stop container: `x abox stop`\n"
}
]
,
"start"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启动一个新的 abox 容器"
,
"en"
:
"Start a new abox container"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"如果不指定容器名称，默认使用 \"abox-0\"。\n使用 --pass 或 --key 时必须指定 --port。\n"
,
"en"
:
"If no container name is specified, \"abox-0\" is used by default.\nWhen using --pass or --key, --port is required.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox start --key <ssh-pubkey-file> --port 2222"
,
"cn"
:
"使用 SSH 公钥启动容器并映射端口"
,
"en"
:
"Start container with SSH public key and port mapping"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox rm"
,
"cn"
:
"删除默认容器"
,
"en"
:
"Remove default container"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox start"
,
"cn"
:
"启动默认容器（无 SSH）"
,
"en"
:
"Start default container (no SSH)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox start --pass - --port 2222 && ssh -p 2222 ai@localhost"
,
"cn"
:
"使用随机密码启动容器，然后通过 SSH 连接（密码见启动输出）"
,
"en"
:
"Start container with random password and connect via SSH (see startup output for password)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox start --key ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub --port 2223 -n mybox && ssh -p 2223 -i ~/.ssh/id_rsa ai@localhost"
,
"cn"
:
"使用 SSH 公钥启动名为 mybox 的容器，然后使用对应私钥连接"
,
"en"
:
"Start container named mybox with SSH public key and connect using the corresponding private key"
}
]
,
"--key"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"SSH 公钥文件路径（需要 --port）"
,
"en"
:
"SSH public key file path (requires --port)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"公钥文件路径"
,
"en"
:
"Public key file path"
}
,
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
}
,
"--pass"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"SSH 密码（需要 --port，使用 \"-\" 自动生成随机密码）"
,
"en"
:
"SSH password (requires --port, use \"-\" to auto-generate random password)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"密码或 \"-\""
,
"en"
:
"Password or \"-\""
}
}
}
,
"--port|-p"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"SSH 端口映射（主机端口）"
,
"en"
:
"SSH port mapping (host port)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"端口号"
,
"en"
:
"Port number"
}
}
}
,
"--name|-n"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称"
,
"en"
:
"Container name"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称（默认为 abox-0）"
,
"en"
:
"Container name (defaults to abox-0)"
}
}
}
}
,
"stop"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"停止指定的 abox 容器"
