,
"pause"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"暂停指定的 abox 容器"
,
"en"
:
"Pause the specified abox container"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"暂停容器会冻结其进程，但不停止容器。\n如果不指定容器名称，默认暂停名为 \"abox-0\" 的容器。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Pausing container freezes its processes without stopping it.\nIf no container name is specified, pauses the container named \"abox-0\" by default.\n"
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称（可选，默认为 abox-0）"
,
"en"
:
"Container name (optional, defaults to abox-0)"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox pause"
,
"cn"
:
"暂停默认容器"
,
"en"
:
"Pause the default container"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox pause mybox"
,
"cn"
:
"暂停名为 mybox 的容器"
,
"en"
:
"Pause container named mybox"
}
]
}
,
"resume"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"恢复指定的 abox 容器"
,
"en"
:
"Resume the specified abox container"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"恢复被暂停的容器，继续运行其进程。\n如果不指定容器名称，默认恢复名为 \"abox-0\" 的容器。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Resumes a paused container and continues its processes.\nIf no container name is specified, resumes the container named \"abox-0\" by default.\n"
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称（可选，默认为 abox-0）"
,
"en"
:
"Container name (optional, defaults to abox-0)"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox resume"
,
"cn"
:
"恢复默认容器"
,
"en"
:
"Resume the default container"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox resume mybox"
,
"cn"
:
"恢复名为 mybox 的容器"
,
"en"
:
"Resume container named mybox"
}
]
}
,
