"强制删除容器，即使容器正在运行。\n如果不指定容器名称，默认删除名为 \"abox-0\" 的容器。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Force removes container even if it's running.\nIf no container name is specified, removes the container named \"abox-0\" by default.\n"
}
]
,
"-n|--name"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称"
,
"en"
:
"Container name"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称（默认为 abox-0）"
,
"en"
:
"Container name (defaults to abox-0)"
}
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称"
,
"en"
:
"Container name"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox rm"
,
"cn"
:
"删除默认容器 abox-0"
,
"en"
:
"Remove the default container abox-0"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox rm mybox"
,
"cn"
:
"删除名为 mybox 的容器"
,
"en"
:
"Remove container named mybox"
}
]
}
,
"ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出所有 abox 容器"
,
"en"
:
"List all abox containers"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"列出所有名称以 \"abox-\" 开头的容器。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Lists all containers whose names start with \"abox-\".\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox ls"
,
"cn"
:
"列出所有 abox 容器"
,
"en"
:
"List all abox containers"
}
]
}
,
"fz"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用 FZF 交互式选择 abox 容器"
,
"en"
:
"Interactively select abox containers using FZF"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"启动 FZF 界面，可以通过模糊搜索选择容器进行操作。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Launches FZF interface for fuzzy searching and selecting containers.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox fz"
,
"cn"
:
"启动 FZF 交互式选择容器"
,
"en"
:
"Launch FZF for interactive container selection"
}
]
}
,
"tmux|t"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"通过 tmux 连接到容器"
,
"en"
:
"Connect to container via tmux"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"在容器中启动一个 tmux 会话，适合长时间运行的交互式任务。\n如果不指定容器名称，默认连接名为 \"abox-0\" 的容器。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Starts a tmux session in the container, suitable for long-running interactive tasks.\nIf no container name is specified, connects to container named \"abox-0\" by default.\n"
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称（可选，默认为 abox-0）"
,
"en"
:
"Container name (optional, defaults to abox-0)"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox tmux"
,
"cn"
:
"通过 tmux 连接到默认容器"
,
"en"
:
"Connect to default container via tmux"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox t mybox"
,
"cn"
:
"通过 tmux 连接到名为 mybox 的容器（简写）"
,
"en"
:
"Connect to container named mybox via tmux (short form)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox t mybox:claude"
,
"cn"
:
"通过 tmux 连接到名为 mybox 的容器中并启动名为 claude 的 tmux 会话"
,
"en"
:
"Connect to container named mybox via tmux and start a tmux session named claude"
}
]
}
,
"cmd"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"在容器中执行命令（非交互式）"
,
"en"
:
"Execute command in container (non-interactive)"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"在指定容器中执行命令，不分配 TTY。\n如果不指定命令，默认执行 bash。\n如果不指定容器名称，默认使用名为 \"abox-0\" 的容器。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Executes command in specified container without allocating TTY.\nIf no command is specified, defaults to bash.\nIf no container name is specified, uses container named \"abox-0\" by default.\n"
}
]
,
"-n|--name"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称"
,
"en"
:
"Container name"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称（默认为 abox-0）"
,
"en"
:
"Container name (defaults to abox-0)"
}
}
}
,
"-r|--root"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 root 用户执行命令"
,
"en"
:
"Execute command as root user"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要执行的命令"
,
"en"
:
"Command to execute"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox cmd -n mybox ls -la"
,
"cn"
:
"在 mybox 容器中执行 ls -la"
,
"en"
:
"Execute ls -la in mybox container"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox cmd -r apt update"
,
"cn"
:
"在默认容器中以 root 执行 apt update"
,
"en"
:
"Execute apt update as root in default container"
}
]
}
,
"cmdi"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"在容器中执行命令（交互式）"
,
"en"
:
"Execute command in container (interactive)"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"在指定容器中交互式执行命令，分配 TTY。\n如果不指定命令，默认执行 bash。\n如果不指定容器名称，默认使用名为 \"abox-0\" 的容器。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Executes command in specified container interactively with TTY allocated.\nIf no command is specified, defaults to bash.\nIf no container name is specified, uses container named \"abox-0\" by default.\n"
}
]
,
"-n|--name"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称"
,
"en"
:
"Container name"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称（默认为 abox-0）"
,
"en"
:
"Container name (defaults to abox-0)"
}
}
}
,
"-r|--root"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 root 用户执行命令"
,
"en"
:
"Execute command as root user"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要执行的命令"
,
"en"
:
"Command to execute"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox cmdi -n mybox bash"
,
"cn"
:
"在 mybox 容器中启动交互式 bash"
,
"en"
:
"Start interactive bash in mybox container"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox cmdi -r bash"
,
"cn"
:
"在默认容器中以 root 启动交互式 bash"
,
"en"
:
"Start interactive bash as root in default container"
}
]
}
,
"login"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"登录到容器（启动 bash）"
,
"en"
:
"Login to container (start bash)"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"在容器中启动一个 bash shell，用于直接操作容器。\n如果不指定容器名称，默认登录名为 \"abox-0\" 的容器。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Starts a bash shell in the container for direct operation.\nIf no container name is specified, logs into container named \"abox-0\" by default.\n"
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"容器名称（可选，默认为 abox-0）"
,
"en"
:
"Container name (optional, defaults to abox-0)"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox login"
,
"cn"
:
"登录到默认容器"
,
"en"
:
"Login to default container"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox login mybox"
,
"cn"
:
"登录到名为 mybox 的容器"
,
"en"
:
"Login to container named mybox"
}
]
}
,
"clearall"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"停止并删除所有 abox 容器和镜像"
,
"en"
:
"Stop and remove all abox containers and images"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"此命令会：\n1. 停止所有名称以 \"abox-\" 开头的容器\n2. 删除所有名称以 \"abox-\" 开头的容器\n3. 删除 abox 镜像\n\n注意：此操作不可逆，请谨慎使用。\n"
,
"en"
:
"This command will:\n1. Stop all containers with names starting with \"abox-\"\n2. Remove all containers with names starting with \"abox-\"\n3. Remove the abox image\n\nWarning: This operation is irreversible, use with caution.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x abox clearall"
,
"cn"
:
"清理所有 abox 容器和镜像"
,
"en"
:
"Clean up all abox containers and images"
}
]
}
,
